data.description: Nestled in the heart of Payson, this well-maintained single story site-built house is a true gem, offering the perfect blend of comfort, style, and natural beauty.  The open concept living area is perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. The high ceilings and abundant natural light create an airy and inviting atmosphere.  As we go into the winter months, imagine enjoying countless hours cozying up to the beautiful fireplace.  The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar. It's a chef's delight and ideal for preparing delicious meals for loved ones.  This home boasts 3 bedrooms, each with ample closet space and windows that flood the rooms with natural light.   The master ...CLICK ''MORE'' bedroom includes an ensuite bathroom for added convenience and privacy.  Step outside to the backyard deck which is the perfect spot for sipping your morning coffee, hosting BBQs, or simply unwinding.  Protect your vehicles from the elements and store your outdoor gear in the attached two-car garage. It offers work benches and plenty of storage.  The home has additional storage underneath it which is easily accessible.  The home has a new roof as of 9/2023.  The water heater is approximately 3 years old.  For those who do not want an HOA but there is a pride of ownership, this is it.  Don't miss the chance to make it your home.
